PACIFIC STATES SAVINGS & LOAN ASS’N v. Henry Douglas INGHRAM, Debtor. No. 8233. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. June 14, 1937. John L. Mace, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. H. D. Inghram, in pro. per.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and MATHEWS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal herein dismissed; that a decree of dismissal be filed md entered accordingly; and the mandate if this court issued forthwith.
